      "content": "Wait, what? Goblins? I'm just asking about flight connections and transit times through Dubai or Doha. Can you please just give me the actual logistical advice? Like, which hub generally has better reliability and faster transit connections for flights heading into Singapore? I don't need metaphors, I just need to know which route is statistically more likely to get me there soonest.",
